## Key Design Decisions

1. **Theme replaces light/dark toggle** — The 3 themes subsume the old system. `t3-dark` is the default, `t3-light` serves the light mode need, `t3-midnight` adds variety. System preference auto-detection is dropped for simplicity (can be re-added later as a "System" meta-theme).

